              <p class="mk-mock-pdf-p"><b>Abstract.</b> We propose a new architecture based solely on attention mechanisms, dispensing with recurrence entirely. Experiments on two machine translation tasks show it to be superior in quality.</p>
              <div class="mk-mock-pdf-h2">1. Introduction</div>
              <p class="mk-mock-pdf-p">Recurrent models have long dominated sequence transduction tasks. The Transformer allows for significantly more parallelization.</p>
