<%!-- FAQ ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── --%>
<section id="faq" class="mk-section">
  <div class="mk-container">
    <p class="mk-eyebrow mk-reveal">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="mk-section-h mk-reveal">Questions, answered.</h2>
    <div class="mk-faq mk-reveal-group">
      <details class="mk-faq-item">
        <summary>Do I need to install anything? <span class="mk-faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>No. Typster runs entirely in the browser. The Typst compiler is bundled in our edge runtime; you just write and hit save.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="mk-faq-item">
        <summary>Can I bring my own fonts? <span class="mk-faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>Yes. Upload TTF or OTF files into a project; Typst will read them on every compile run.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="mk-faq-item">
        <summary>Is there a desktop app? <span class="mk-faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>A desktop build is on the roadmap. The web app is already keyboard-first and works offline once loaded.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="mk-faq-item">
        <summary>How does pricing work for students? <span class="mk-faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>The free plan is unlimited for personal use. Email us with a .edu address for a free year of Pro.</p>
      </details>
      <details class="mk-faq-item">
        <summary>Is my work private? <span class="mk-faq-icon">+</span></summary>
        <p>Projects are private by default. Sharing is opt-in and revocable, per project, per link.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

